  • Method Details

    • fail

      public static FailoverHandlingResult fail()
      Fail the failover process (i.e. leave the task in the failed state and do not retry failover on this task). Such a task will require manual intervention!

    • postpone

      unit - duration granularity type
      duration - duration value

    • complete
